1. run `./configure`

2. run `make` to compile

3. run `make install` as root

4. if desired, run `mkdir ~/.tile`

5. if desired, run `cp /usr/local/share/tile/wmprofiles /usr/local/share/tile/wmavoid ~/.tile/` and edit the files

6. when run, if you do not want to use complete full screen, use the "-p" with one
   of the values from wmprofiles. also, use -m or -w for multi-desktop operation.

